Run koji_install.sh for setup kojihub, kojiweb, kojid and kojira on one host.
Please read a what script tell!

Run add-remote-dist.sh for setup one dist, examle: sh add-remote-dist.sh fedora 14
where fedora - is a distr part, 14 - it version of distr. This is raw script.

Run koji-uninstall.sh for delete and clear packages and configurations.
